<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16026</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘很想哭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16027</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她很害怕，很饿，也很孤单。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不会哭的。”她大声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31007</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“至少我是自由的。没有人想要抓我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31008</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她感觉好一点了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘流浪了很多天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在森林里生存不是一件容易的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>下雨的时候拇指姑娘把树叶当做伞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>晚上她睡在树根软软的苔藓上面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每天早上，拇指姑娘用草上的露水洗脸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后她会爬到一朵花上面吃一两朵花瓣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71031</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“每天都吃花，我已经厌烦了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她边说边咬着一朵百合花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74430</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“厌烦了吃花？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只有黑点的红虫子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80294</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84049</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，对不起。”拇指姑娘说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没有看到你。我会到另一朵花那里去的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是一只瓢虫。我不吃花。”那只虫子说，“我吃小昆虫。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105143</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要吃我！我不是昆虫。我是拇指姑娘。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105144</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的名字叫瓢虫小姐。”瓢虫大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116092</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你想吃这些昆虫吗？他们很好吃的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121016</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不用了，谢谢。”拇指姑娘马上回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121017</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126150</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“蓝莓怎么样？”瓢虫小姐笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126151</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以带你去它们生长的地方，跟我来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘拍了拍手说，“好啊，谢谢你！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然瓢虫张开翅膀，准备飞翔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>百合花开始前后摇晃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘失去平衡，从花上掉了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”她落在了一个沙丘上，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161347</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后从一个黑暗的隧道里滑了下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161348</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165229</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“敌情警报！”有人大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165230</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170762</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘在一个蚂蚁窝里面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175016</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很多蚂蚁们像士兵一样排着队。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175017</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个大蚂蚁指着她说，“快给我出去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187559</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我……刚才……。”拇指姑娘结结巴巴地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们必须保卫我们的女王。向前进！”蚂蚁大声地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“求求你了，这是一个误会。我会出去的。”拇指姑娘大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200159</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她尝试着从那个隧道爬上去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“沙子太滑了！”她泄气地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“抓住敌人！”蚂蚁们大声地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220040</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘终于爬了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她往后看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蚂蚁们像黑色的波浪向她涌来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我该怎么办？”她大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232946</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“继续前进！”大蚂蚁对其它蚂蚁大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243357</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘转身飞速地逃跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243358</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太多蚂蚁了！”她大叫，不敢再往后看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257344</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，拇指姑娘看见一棵树上有一个小洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257345</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她跑进去，用一片掉下来的叶子把自己藏起来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们应该找不到我的。”她喘着气说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蚂蚁们绕过树走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们的声音逐渐消失。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后拇指姑娘听不见他们的声音了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘终于暂时安全了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>